{
  "text": "is a 3N × 3N-matrix with nine diagonal submatrices containing the cross-section inertia parameters (36) By inverting the compliance matrix D i , we finally get the expression of the stiffness matrix K i * in the local system of the i-th bracing with open thin-walled cross-section (37) that, introduced in Eq. (10), permits bracings with open thin-walled cross-sections to be considered in the general formulation proposed by [CITATION_1] .",
